task.summary: changed to binary tree with segments: - segments have lower boxes count inside them vastly improving insert&remove - boxes can be crossing into multiple segments (max 4 if box size is always guaranteed to be always lower than segment size) - for 99% of boxes that are in only 1 segment update is faster - segments do automatic splits and merges when boxes count pass low or high threshold (slow but occurs rarely) Pair manager for storing overlapping boxes: - fast hash table with linear vectors
Removed PairManager, used HashSet from base lib
changes for new typedefs removed warnings
updated for new clion build dir structure added emscripten build for linux
